IMAPAccount mailboxorg
Host imap.mailbox.org
UserCmd "pass mailbox.org/email"
PassCmd "pass mailbox.org/password"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore mailboxorg-remote
Account mailboxorg

MaildirStore mailboxorg-local
SubFolders Verbatim
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/mails/
Inbox ~/mails/Inbox

Channel mailboxorg
Far :mailboxorg-remote:
Near :mailboxorg-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *